{"tid":2322891,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE全體褲裝帥爆！　MINA「西裝＋紅唇」韓網驚嘆：美瘋了","createTime":"2020-12-12T16:50:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T17:01:17.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2a21d780dc123c933849d1b6e99b580003ba69b5","tid":2322891,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T16:50:57.000Z","msg":"南韓音樂盛典「The Fact Music Awards」（TMA）12日晚間7點在首爾舉行，因應疫情，紅毯和演出皆採取事先錄製的方式。TWICE因成員定延修養、以及SANA正在隔離中，雖然只有7人出席，但選擇穿上褲裝和西服，氣勢鎮壓全場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5330/d5330953.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5330%2Fd5330953.jpg&h=4ce0b8f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「The Fact Music Awards」TWICE舞台走帥氣風。（圖／翻攝自演出畫面）<br />\n<br />\nTWICE出席「The Fact Music Awards」走帥氣風，成員全都選擇褲裝，甚至在超低溫的首爾穿上激短褲，不畏寒冷的露出美腿。成員MINA以西裝搭配俐落髮型和紅唇的模樣，更上了南韓論壇的熱門貼文，紛紛稱讚她：「好像是沒見過的氛圍，太美了。」、「好像是黑化的主角一樣又帥又美，瘋了！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5330/d5330949.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5330%2Fd5330949.jpg&h=ca5bb07e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲MINA西裝搭紅唇美翻韓網。（圖／翻攝自演出畫面）<br />\n<br />\nTWICE一連帶來《MORE &amp; MORE》和《I CAN'T STOP ME》等歌曲的舞台，並獲得年度藝人獎。娜璉代表發表感言，除了感謝公司同事外，也沒忘記感謝粉絲：「是因為ONCE（粉絲暱稱）我們才能拿到這麼好的獎，謝謝ONCE。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5330/d5330950.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5330%2Fd5330950.jpg&h=c26fbf16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5330/d5330951.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5330%2Fd5330951.jpg&h=0ec5bf88&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c207da39c01d27a8718227d5cf656edd46908b6","tid":2322891,"uid":256796,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T16:51:46.000Z","msg":"不了⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da